      <title>塔塔与和硕就在印度泰米尔纳德邦组装 iPhone 的合作进行谈判 - 消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tata-pegatron-partnership-talks-iphone-assembly-indias-tamil-nadu-sources-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位直接了解此事的消息人士周四表示，塔塔集团正在与台湾和硕进行深入谈判，以建立合作伙伴关系，运营这家印度公司正在南部泰米尔纳德邦建设的 iPhone 组装厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tata-pegatron-partnership-talks-iphone-assembly-indias-tamil-nadu-sources-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 14:40:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸前领导人昂山素季儿子表示，患病的缅甸前领导人昂山素季在单独监禁中“精神状态良好”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ailing-myanmar-ex-leader-suu-kyi-good-spirits-solitary-says-son-media-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，缅甸被拘留的前领导人、民主偶像昂山素季的儿子表示，昂山素季在单独监禁中精神状态良好，“即使她的健康状况不如过去”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ailing-myanmar-ex-leader-suu-kyi-good-spirits-solitary-says-son-media-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 14:28:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型央行正转向降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/big-central-banks-are-pivoting-towards-rate-cuts-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[主要央行现在表示，随着通胀走弱，未来几个月利率可能会走低，呼吁结束数十年来最激进的紧缩周期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/big-central-banks-are-pivoting-towards-rate-cuts-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 13:44:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国议员敦促对缅甸采取人道主义行动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-press-humanitarian-action-myanmar-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份声明称，众议院议员周四将启动首次缅甸问题两党核心小组，以迫使美国政府对这个东南亚国家自三年前军方发动政变以来的危机采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-press-humanitarian-action-myanmar-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 13:05:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国制裁缅甸军方相关企业和部门</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-sanctions-myanmar-military-linked-enterprises-divisions-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国周四对参与所谓“严重侵犯人权”和镇压缅甸平民的军事单位和企业实施制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-sanctions-myanmar-military-linked-enterprises-divisions-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 12:36:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>现代汽车将为意大利依维柯提供面向欧洲的新型电动货车</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hyundai-motor-supply-italys-iveco-with-new-electric-van-europe-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[依维柯集团和现代汽车周四表示，已达成协议，韩国集团将向这家意大利卡车和公共汽车制造商提供全电动轻型商用车，扩大了现有的合作伙伴关系协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hyundai-motor-supply-italys-iveco-with-new-electric-van-europe-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 11:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法院裁决前总理伊姆兰·汗泄露秘密电报伤害了巴基斯坦</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ex-pm-imran-khans-leak-secret-cable-hurt-pakistan-court-ruling-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 泄露一份秘密外交电报，对这个南亚国家的经济、政治和外交造成了损害，法庭在周四做出有罪判决并判处他 10 年监禁后发布了一份详细的判决书。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ex-pm-imran-khans-leak-secret-cable-hurt-pakistan-court-ruling-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 08:43:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：以色列袭击后伊朗卫队从叙利亚撤回军官</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-guards-pull-officers-syria-after-israeli-strikes-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五位知情人士称，由于以色列发动一系列致命袭击，伊朗革命卫队已缩减了在叙利亚的高级军官部署，并将更多地依靠什叶派民兵盟军来维持其在叙利亚的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-guards-pull-officers-syria-after-israeli-strikes-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 08:38:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾选出议会议长执政党观点亲中</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-elects-parliament-speaker-ruling-party-views-pro-china-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾议会周四选举最大反对党的前总统候选人为新议长，他将负责接待来访的外国议员，执政党称他是亲中国的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-elects-parliament-speaker-ruling-party-views-pro-china-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 08:26:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯议员称朝鲜代表团将访问莫斯科</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korean-delegation-visit-moscow-russian-lawmaker-says-2024-02-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方通讯社俄新社周四援引反对党共产党一名代表的话说，朝鲜代表团将于 2 月 13 日访问俄罗斯议会下院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korean-delegation-visit-moscow-russian-lawmaker-says-2024-02-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 08:07:07 GMT</pubDate>
